short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ReSpecT extension converters browser requests (HAR) to OpenApi/Swagger specification.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ReSpecT stands for OpenApi Specification Reverse engineering Tool.

This tool helps you to build a specification file based on: 
1. Outgoing browser requests
2. Your own custom API call to any service 

Please fill free to leave any feedback here:
https://github.com/lojell/ReSpecT/issues
